msgstr "Bilah Samping Kontrol Teks Kaya"

msgid "Formatted chat via RichTextControl. Requires restart."
msgstr "Obrolan terformat melalui RichTextControl. Memerlukan mulai ulang."

msgid "Humanizer skill (natural prose)"
msgstr "Keahlian Humanizer (prosa alami)"

msgid ""
"When enabled, injects guidance into the system prompt so the model makes "
"generated or revised document text sound more natural and human (removes AI "
"slop patterns). Edit the rules in your LibreOffice profile under "
"writeragent/skills/humanizer/SKILL.md (the file is auto-created on first "
"use). A dedicated Skills tab can be added later."
msgstr ""
"Saat diaktifkan, menyuntikkan panduan ke dalam prompt sistem agar model "
"membuat teks dokumen yang dihasilkan atau direvisi terdengar lebih alami dan"
" manusiawi (menghapus pola AI yang kaku). Edit aturan di profil LibreOffice "
"Anda di bawah writeragent/skills/humanizer/SKILL.md (file dibuat otomatis "
"saat penggunaan pertama). Tab Keahlian khusus dapat ditambahkan nanti."

msgid "Doc"
msgstr "Dok"

msgid "Enable grammar checker (Writer)"
msgstr "Aktifkan pemeriksa tata bahasa (Writer)"

msgid ""
"Off = disabled. AI (LLM) = use your configured text model/API. LanguageTool "
"= use local LanguageTool server via venv pip package."
msgstr ""
"Mati = dinonaktifkan. AI (LLM) = gunakan model teks/API yang telah Anda "
"konfigurasi. LanguageTool = gunakan server LanguageTool lokal melalui paket "
"pip venv."

msgid "Off"
msgstr "Mati"

msgid "AI (LLM)"
msgstr "AI (LLM)"

msgid "LanguageTool (Local)"
msgstr "LanguageTool (Lokal)"

msgid "Vale (Local Style) (WIP)"
msgstr "Vale (Gaya Lokal) (WIP)"

msgid "Harper"
msgstr "Harper"

msgid "Model (optional)"
msgstr "Model (opsional)"

msgid "Leave empty to use the same text model as chat."
msgstr "Biarkan kosong untuk menggunakan model teks yang sama dengan obrolan."

msgid "Pause grammar while chat/agent runs"
msgstr "Jeda tata bahasa saat obrolan/agen berjalan"

msgid ""
"When on, AI grammar skips background requests while sidebar chat or agent "
"runs, to avoid concurrent API calls."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, tata bahasa AI melewati permintaan latar belakang saat obrolan "
"bilah sisi atau agen berjalan, untuk menghindari panggilan API bersamaan."

msgid "Batch sentences"
msgstr "Batch kalimat"

msgid ""
"Number of sentences to send per LLM request (1-8). 1 (default) is most "
"reliable; higher values are faster and cheaper but may hit token limits or "
"cause model errors."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah kalimat yang dikirim per permintaan LLM (1-8). 1 (default) adalah "
"yang paling andal; nilai yang lebih tinggi lebih cepat dan lebih murah "
"tetapi dapat mencapai batas token atau menyebabkan kesalahan model."

msgid "Concurrent requests"
msgstr "Permintaan serentak"

msgid ""
"Max simultaneous background grammar API calls (1-8). 1 matches prior "
"behavior. Raise for OpenRouter or other providers that allow parallel "
"requests; use with care alongside sidebar chat."
msgstr ""
"Maksimum panggilan API tata bahasa latar belakang secara simultan (1-8). 1 "
"sesuai dengan perilaku sebelumnya. Tingkatkan untuk OpenRouter atau penyedia"
" lain yang mengizinkan permintaan paralel; gunakan dengan hati-hati bersama "
"obrolan bilah samping."

msgid "Sentence language detection"
msgstr "Deteksi bahasa kalimat"

msgid ""
"Verify each complete sentence's language against the document locale. AI "
"uses your grammar/chat API; Local uses bundled langdetect (no API call, no "
"venv). Mismatches update CharLocale and re-check grammar."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi setiap kalimat lengkap terhadap lokal dokumen. AI menggunakan API"
" tata bahasa/obrolan Anda; Lokal menggunakan langdetect bawaan (tanpa "
"panggilan API, tanpa venv). Ketidakcocokan akan memperbarui CharLocale dan "
"memeriksa ulang tata bahasa."

msgid "Local (langdetect)"
msgstr "Lokal (langdetect)"

msgid "Enter key sends sidebar chat message"
msgstr "Tombol Enter mengirim pesan obrolan bilah samping"

msgid ""
"When on, Enter in the sidebar query runs the same action as Send; "
"Shift+Enter inserts a newline. When off, Enter inserts a newline."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, Enter pada kueri bilah samping menjalankan tindakan yang sama "
"dengan Kirim; Shift+Enter menyisipkan baris baru. Saat nonaktif, Enter "
"menyisipkan baris baru."

msgid "Agent edit review"
msgstr "Tinjauan suntingan Agen"

msgid ""
"Off = direct edits. Record = tracked changes you accept/reject yourself. "
"Wait = apply_document_content blocks (on chat/MCP worker thread) until you "
"review."
msgstr ""
"Mati = suntingan langsung. Rekam = perubahan terlacak yang Anda terima/tolak"
" sendiri. Tunggu = apply_document_content memblokir (pada utas pekerja "
"chat/MCP) sampai Anda meninjau."

msgid "Record (track changes)"
msgstr "Rekam (lacak perubahan)"

msgid "Wait for review"
msgstr "Tunggu tinjauan"

msgid "Draw and Impress tools"
msgstr "Alat Draw dan Impress"

msgid "Vector Search"
msgstr "Pencarian Vektor"

msgid "Cross-file search"
msgstr "Pencarian lintas berkas"

msgid ""
"Indexed semantic + keyword search for document_research (corpus.db). "
"Requires embeddings venv — see Python Test."
msgstr ""
"Pencarian semantik + kata kunci terindeks untuk document_research "
"(corpus.db). Memerlukan venv embeddings — lihat Uji Python."

msgid "Embeddings + FTS"
msgstr "Embeddings + FTS"

msgid "LlamaIndex"
msgstr "LlamaIndex"

msgid "Zvec (experimental)"
msgstr "Zvec (eksperimental)"

msgid "LanceDB (experimental)"
msgstr "LanceDB (eksperimental)"

msgid "Embedding Model"
msgstr "Model Penyematan"

msgid "HuggingFace model ID for local provider, or endpoint-specific model ID"
msgstr ""
"ID model HuggingFace untuk penyedia lokal, atau ID model spesifik titik "
"akhir"

msgid "Enable cross-file rerank"
msgstr "Aktifkan rerank lintas berkas"

msgid ""
"Second-stage cross-encoder after hybrid retrieve (Embeddings + FTS and "
"LlamaIndex). Off by default."
msgstr ""
"Cross-encoder tahap kedua setelah pengambilan hibrida (Embeddings + FTS dan "
"LlamaIndex). Nonaktif secara default."

msgid "Rerank model"
msgstr "Model rerank"

msgid ""
"Used only when rerank is enabled. English MiniLM is fast; bge-reranker-v2-m3"
" is multilingual and downloads ~2.3 GB."
msgstr ""
"Hanya digunakan saat rerank diaktifkan. MiniLM bahasa Inggris cepat; bge-"
"reranker-v2-m3 bersifat multibahasa dan mengunduh ~2,3 GB."

msgid "cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2"
msgstr "cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2"

msgid "BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3"
msgstr "BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3"

msgid "Core services (config, events, logging)"
msgstr "Layanan inti (konfigurasi, peristiwa, pencatatan)"

msgid "MCP"
msgstr "MCP"

msgid "Enable MCP Server"
msgstr "Aktifkan Server MCP"

msgid ""
"Localhost only, no auth. Clients use http://localhost:<port>/mcp (streamable"
" HTTP)."
msgstr ""
"Hanya localhost, tanpa autentikasi. Klien menggunakan "
"http://localhost:<port>/mcp (HTTP yang dapat dialirkan)."

msgid "MCP Port"
msgstr "Port MCP"

msgid "MCP Tool Exposure"
msgstr "Eksposur Alat MCP"

msgid ""
"How specialized tools are surfaced to MCP clients. delegate=reached via the "
"delegate gateway (today's behavior); direct_flat=all MCP-reachable "
"specialized tools listed directly, excluding sidebar-only flows (best for "
"clients with their own tool-search); direct_discovery=small core list plus "
"find_tools (domain catalog, then per-domain tool schemas; best for any "
"client)."
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana alat khusus dimunculkan ke klien MCP. delegate=dijangkau melalui "
"gateway delegasi (perilaku saat ini); direct_flat=semua alat khusus yang "
"dapat dijangkau MCP dicantumkan secara langsung, tidak termasuk alur khusus "
"bilah sisi (terbaik untuk klien dengan pencarian alat sendiri); "
"direct_discovery=daftar inti kecil ditambah find_tools (katalog domain, lalu"
" skema alat per domain; terbaik untuk klien mana pun)."

msgid "Delegate (default)"
msgstr "Delegasi (default)"

msgid "Direct — list all tools"
msgstr "Langsung — cantumkan semua alat"

msgid "Direct — discovery (find_tools)"
msgstr "Langsung — penemuan (find_tools)"

msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

msgid "Python venv path"
msgstr "Jalur venv Python"

msgid ""
"If set, runs tools in that venv (bin/python or Scripts/python.exe). If "
"empty, run_venv_python_script uses this process's sys.executable (basic "
"stdlib); use a venv for numpy/pandas and Vision Helpers (paddleocr, "
"paddlepaddle)."
msgstr ""
"Jika diatur, menjalankan alat di venv tersebut (bin/python atau "
"Scripts/python.exe). Jika kosong, run_venv_python_script menggunakan "
"sys.executable proses ini (stdlib dasar); gunakan venv untuk numpy/pandas "
"dan Pembantu Vision (paddleocr, paddlepaddle)."

msgid "Test"
msgstr "Uji"

msgid "Python script timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Batas waktu skrip Python (detik)"

msgid ""
"Wall-clock limit for Run Python Script, =PYTHON(), and "
"run_venv_python_script."
msgstr ""
"Batas waktu dinding (wall-clock) untuk Jalankan Skrip Python, =PYTHON(), dan"
" run_venv_python_script."

msgid "Max Calc data cells"
msgstr "Jumlah sel data Calc maksimum"

msgid ""
"Maximum cells in =PYTHON() data or Run Python Script data/data_range. Larger"
" values use more RAM and time; UNO range read still dominates."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah sel maksimum dalam data =PYTHON() atau data/data_range Jalankan Skrip"
" Python. Nilai yang lebih besar menggunakan lebih banyak RAM dan waktu; "
"pembacaan rentang UNO tetap yang paling dominan."

msgid "Python session mode"
msgstr "Mode sesi Python"

msgid ""
"Isolated: each =PYTHON() cell gets a fresh namespace. Shared: one namespace "
"per workbook (variables carry between cells)."
msgstr ""
"Terisolasi: setiap sel =PYTHON() mendapatkan namespace baru. Berbagi: satu "
"namespace per buku kerja (variabel terbawa antar sel)."

msgid "Isolated (default)"
msgstr "Terisolasi (bawaan)"

msgid "Shared kernel"
msgstr "Kernel berbagi"

msgid "Python auto spill in Calc"
msgstr "Python auto spill di Calc"

msgid ""
"Automatically spill multi-cell array/DataFrame results from =PYTHON() into "
"adjacent cells."
msgstr ""
"Secara otomatis menumpahkan hasil array/DataFrame multi-sel dari =PYTHON() "
"ke sel yang berdekatan."

msgid "Convert Date/Time and Timedelta Strings"
msgstr "Konversi String Tanggal/Waktu dan Timedelta"

msgid ""
"Automatically detect and convert date/time and duration strings to "
"datetime/timedelta objects when sending data to the Python worker. Requires "
"the 'pandas' and 'dateparser' packages in your venv."
msgstr ""
"Mendeteksi dan mengonversi string tanggal/waktu dan durasi secara otomatis "
"menjadi objek datetime/timedelta saat mengirim data ke worker Python. "
"Memerlukan paket 'pandas' dan 'dateparser' di venv Anda."

msgid "PPT-Master data path"
msgstr "Jalur data PPT-Master"

msgid ""
"Path to the ppt-master skill tree (SKILL.md, templates/, "
"scripts/svg_to_pptx/). Clone https://github.com/hugohe3/ppt-master and point"
" here at .../ppt-master/skills/ppt-master. Leave empty to auto-detect (dev "
"clone beside repo, then env)."
msgstr ""
"Jalur ke pohon keterampilan ppt-master (SKILL.md, templates/, "
"scripts/svg_to_pptx/). Klon https://github.com/hugohe3/ppt-master dan "
"arahkan ke sini di .../ppt-master/skills/ppt-master. Biarkan kosong untuk "
"deteksi otomatis (klon pengembangan di samping repositori, lalu env)."

msgid "Vision / OCR"
msgstr "Vision / OCR"

msgid "Image scale"
msgstr "Skala gambar"

msgid "Upscale before OCR/layout. Try 2.0 for small screenshots."
msgstr ""
"Tingkatkan skala sebelum OCR/tata letak. Coba 2.0 untuk tangkapan layar "
"kecil."

msgid "Worker timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Batas waktu pekerja (detik)"

msgid "Host subprocess limit for Vision Helpers (first model download)."
msgstr ""
"Batas subproses host untuk Vision Helpers (pengunduhan model pertama)."

msgid "Docling artifacts path"
msgstr "Jalur artefak Docling"

msgid "Optional folder from docling-tools models download (offline use)."
msgstr "Folder opsional dari unduhan model docling-tools (penggunaan luring)."

msgid "OCR confidence threshold"
msgstr "Ambang batas kepercayaan OCR"

msgid "RapidOCR minimum text score. Raise to reduce garbage text."
msgstr "Skor teks minimum RapidOCR. Tingkatkan untuk mengurangi teks sampah."

msgid "OCR entire image"
msgstr "OCR seluruh gambar"

msgid "Recommended for embedded graphics exported from LibreOffice."
msgstr ""
"Direkomendasikan untuk grafik tertanam yang diekspor dari LibreOffice."

msgid "Table extraction mode"
msgstr "Mode ekstraksi tabel"

msgid "Accurate (default)"
msgstr "Akurat (default)"

msgid "Fast"
msgstr "Cepat"

msgid "Table cell matching"
msgstr "Pencocokan sel tabel"

msgid "Align detected table cells with content (extract_structure)."
msgstr ""
"Sejajarkan sel tabel yang terdeteksi dengan konten (extract_structure)."

msgid "Keep orphan text clusters"
msgstr "Pertahankan klaster teks yatim"

msgid "Group unassigned text into clusters for messy layouts."
msgstr ""
"Kelompokkan teks yang tidak ditetapkan ke dalam klaster untuk tata letak "
"yang berantakan."

msgid "Document insert mode"
msgstr "Mode sisip dokumen"

msgid ""
"html = Docling HTML import (default). structured = bbox column layout in "
"Writer; native Calc cells for extract_structure tables."
msgstr ""
"html = Impor HTML Docling (bawaan). structured = tata letak kolom bbox di "
"Writer; sel Calc asli untuk tabel extract_structure."

msgid "Standard HTML"
msgstr "HTML Standar"

msgid "Structured (layout / cell grid)"
msgstr "Terstruktur (tata letak / kisi sel)"

msgid "Layout model"
msgstr "Model tata letak"

msgid "Heron (default)"
msgstr "Heron (default)"

msgid "Egret large (slower"
msgstr "Egret large (lebih lambat"

msgid "Extract formulas (LaTeX)"
msgstr "Ekstrak rumus (LaTeX)"

msgid "Opt-in. Downloads extra VLM models on first use; slower."
msgstr ""
"Ikut serta. Mengunduh model VLM tambahan saat penggunaan pertama; lebih "
"lambat."

msgid "Code block enrichment"
msgstr "Pengayaan blok kode"

msgid "Specialized OCR for code/terminal screenshots."
msgstr "OCR khusus untuk tangkapan layar kode/terminal."

msgid "Docling document timeout (s)"
msgstr "Batas waktu dokumen Docling (detik)"

msgid "Per-conversion timeout inside Docling. 0 = no limit."
msgstr "Batas waktu per konversi di dalam Docling. 0 = tanpa batas."
